data.description: Welcome to this newly renovated! This stunning home offers a comfortable and modern living experience. The first floor boasts an inviting living room, a spacious dining area, and a beautifully designed kitchen. The kitchen features sleek white cabinets, complemented by stylish black handles. The stainless steel appliances add a touch of elegance, while the granite countertops and the beautiful backsplash provide a perfect blend of functionality and sophistication.  Moving upstairs, you will discover three well-appointed bedrooms, offering ample space for rest and relaxation. The full bathroom on the top floor is tastefully designed, providing convenience and comfort for the entire household.  The basement of this property is semi-finished, offering versatility and potential for various uses. With a convenient half bathroom and plenty of storage space, it provides the perfect balance between functionality and practicality.  This listing presents a wonderful opportunity to own a newly renovated home that combines modern aesthetics with thoughtful design. Don't miss out on the chance to make this property your own and enjoy a comfortable lifestyle in a desirable location. Schedule a showing and experience the charm of this remarkable property firsthand!
